# OR Books Stencil theme

When working under `orbooks-theme/`, read **`docs/agents/stencil-theme.md`** first.

## Hard rules

- Run Stencil CLI from `orbooks-theme/`.
- Never commit or echo `secrets.stencil.json` / access tokens.
- Store URL = storefront homepage (`https://www.orbooks.com`), not the API `/v3/` path.
- This theme is **not** Briefboard (`app/`). Prefer separate git repo; do not mix theme dumps into Briefboard history without an explicit user decision.

## Common commands

```bash
stencil --help
stencil debug
stencil start
stencil download -o
stencil pull
stencil bundle
stencil push          # upload only
stencil push -a       # upload + activate
```

Full command list + Helvetica cutover notes: `docs/agents/stencil-theme.md`.
